{"builtWith":"0.15.15","comments":[{"LineComment":" ━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━"},{"LineComment":"                        // hydrogen // element // compound // canvas // grid3d"},{"LineComment":" ━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━"},{"LineComment":" | Canvas Grid3D — 3D grid system for motion graphics and VFX."},{"LineComment":" |"},{"LineComment":" | ## Design Philosophy"},{"LineComment":" |"},{"LineComment":" | Professional 3D tools (professional motion graphics and 3D tools) require:"},{"LineComment":" |"},{"LineComment":" | 1. **World Origin (0,0,0)** — Center of 3D space"},{"LineComment":" | 2. **World Planes** — XY (floor), XZ (front), YZ (side)"},{"LineComment":" | 3. **Bounded Extent** — Grid doesn't extend to infinity"},{"LineComment":" | 4. **Orthographic Views** — Top, Front, Side, Perspective"},{"LineComment":" | 5. **Axis Coloring** — X=Red, Y=Green, Z=Blue (RGB convention)"},{"LineComment":" |"},{"LineComment":" | ## Bounded Parameters"},{"LineComment":" |"},{"LineComment":" | - **GridSpacing3D**: 1 to 10000 units (same as 2D)"},{"LineComment":" | - **GridExtent**: 1 to 100000 units from origin"},{"LineComment":" | - **Subdivisions**: 1 to 10 per major cell"},{"LineComment":" |"},{"LineComment":" | ## Coordinate System"},{"LineComment":" |"},{"LineComment":" | Uses right-handed coordinates:"},{"LineComment":" | - **X**: Right (Red axis)"},{"LineComment":" | - **Y**: Up (Green axis)"},{"LineComment":" | - **Z**: Toward viewer / out of screen (Blue axis)"},{"LineComment":" |"},{"LineComment":" | ## Module Structure"},{"LineComment":" |"},{"LineComment":" | This is a leader module that re-exports from submodules:"},{"LineComment":" | - Types: GridExtent, WorldPlane, Axis"},{"LineComment":" | - Config: Grid3DConfig and builders"},{"LineComment":" | - Snap: SnapPoint3D and operations"},{"LineComment":" | - Lines: GridLine3D type"},{"LineComment":" | - Geometry: Grid